  "about": "Emporio is an observant, timid boy who was born within the walls of Green Dolphin Street Prison. Despite having grown up in such a harsh environment, Emporio prefers to avoid any conflict. Emporio also frequently advises others to do the same, such as when he first reveals himself to Jolyne, warning her of approaching danger.\n\n\n\nEven though Emporio doesn’t share the offensive skills of Jolyne or others, he remains extremely knowledgeable for his young age and proves his intelligence many times.",
